## What This Is

OpenElara Cloud is:
- üéì An **educational demonstration** of sovereign cloud AI architecture
- üî¨ A **proof of concept** for BYOK + BYOC (Bring Your Own Key + Cloud)
- üõ†Ô∏è A **hobbyist project** that grew into something useful
- üí° A **vision** of how AI could work: user-controlled, self-hosted

## BYOK + BYOC Philosophy

**Bring Your Own Key (BYOK):**
- You provide your own API keys (Together.ai, OpenRouter, OpenAI, etc.)
- You pay AI providers directly at their rates
- Your keys stay in YOUR browser - never on our servers

**Bring Your Own Cloud (BYOC):**
- You deploy to YOUR Firebase project
- Your data lives in YOUR Firestore
- Your files go to YOUR Firebase Storage
- You control everything

We don't charge for the app. We don't take a cut. It's your infrastructure.

